 dispatch automation, no named technicians on the website. A bolt-on operator could: (a) launch a Plumb Sentinel monthly membership at $24.95/mo across existing customer base = $300-600K incremental ARR within 12 months; (b) migrate to ServiceTitan for dispatch + scheduling = 15-25% windshield-time reduction; (c) build a technic','medium',0.75),
